OL,3,CLegacy body sorry after data breach
OL,5,FThe body tasked with investigating
OL,6,Foutstanding cases from the Northern
OL,7,FIreland Troubles has apologised
OL,8,Ffollowing a data breach.
OL,10,FThe Independent Commission for
OL,11,FReconciliation and Information
OL,12,FRecovery (ICRIR) said the names of 25
OL,13,Fpeople who had contacted it had been
OL,14,Fmistakenly disclosed to an individual.
OL,16,FThe commission said no sensitive
OL,17,Finformation had been disclosed but
OL,18,Fsaid an internal investigation is now
OL,19,Funder way.
