OL,3,CLegacy body sorry after data breach
OL,5,FThe ICRIR was created by the
OL,6,FConservative government's Legacy Act
OL,7,Fwhich halted scores of civil cases and
OL,8,Finquests into Troubles deaths.
OL,10,FBereaved families, victims and certain
OL,11,Fpublic authorities can instead request
OL,12,Fthe ICRIR carry out an investigation.
OL,14,FWhile Labour has committed to
OL,15,Frepealing the Act and has said legacy
OL,16,Finquests will resume, it is continuing
OL,17,Fwith the ICRIR.
