OL,3,CLegacy body sorry after data breach
OL,5,FThe ICRIR has been opposed by victims'
OL,6,Forganisations and political parties in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland and its powers have
OL,8,Fbeen subject to legal challenges.
OL,10,FThe body is headed up by Northern
OL,11,FIreland's former Lord Chief Justice
OL,12,FSir Declan Morgan.
OL,14,FThe ICRIR said it experienced a
OL,15,F"limited data breach" on the afternoon
OL,16,Fof March 18.
