OL,3,CLegacy body sorry after data breach
OL,5,FA statement said: "The names of 25
OL,6,Fpeople, principally Requesting
OL,7,FIndividuals (RI), were mistakenly
OL,8,Fdisclosed to a single recipient who
OL,9,Fhad previously sought assistance from
OL,10,Fthe Commission.
OL,12,F"This was caused by an administrative
OL,13,Ferror in an email address field.
OL,15,F"No sensitive or special category
OL,16,Finformation was disclosed.
OL,18,F"The mistake was discovered within
OL,19,Fseveral hours and addressed swiftly.
